data.title: List of Film Genres and Sub-Genres: PDF Handout
data.meta_description: 9_film_genres_and_sub-genres_e - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document lists numerous film genres and subgenres, including action/adventure, comedy, crime/gangster, cult, and drama as some of the main genres. Under each genre are then listed various specific subgenres that fall under that category, such as buddy cop films, heist films, and mob films under crime/gangster genre. The document appears to be adapted from an external source listing different film genre and subgenre types.
